Package com.biorecorder.edflib

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EdfFileReader
    Permits to read data samples from EDF or BDF file.
    EdfFileWriter
    This class permits to write digital or physical samples from multiple measuring channel to EDF or BDF File.
    EdfFilter
    A base decorator class (pattern Decorator) that is actually just a wrapper around some other EdfWriter object.
    EdfJoiner
    Permits to join (piece together) given number of incoming DataRecords.
    EdfSignalsFilter
    Permits to realize some kind of transformation (digital filtering) with the data samples belonging to some signals (add digital filters to some signals).
    EdfSignalsRemover
    Permit to omit samples from some channels (delete signals)
    EdfWriter
    This abstract class is the superclass of all classes representing an output stream of DataRecords.
    EndianBitConverter
    Contains several useful static methods to convert Java integer (32-bit, signed, BIG_ENDIAN) to an array of bytes (BIG_ENDIAN or LITTLE_ENDIAN ordered) and vice versa
    HeaderInfo
    This class permits to store the information required for the header record of EDF/BDF file and then correctly extract data from the file.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FileType
    Defines file types that can be read or written by EdfFileReader and EdfFileWriter
